column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?continent ?river ?continentLabel ?riverLabel WHERE {   {     SELECT ?continent (MAX(?length) AS ?length_)     WHERE     {       ?river wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q355304;              wdt:P2043 ?length;              wdt:P30 ?continent.     }     GROUP BY ?continent   }   ?river wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q355304;          wdt:P2043 ?length;          wdt:P30 ?continent. ?continent rdfs:label ?continentLabel . FILTER (LANG(?continentLabel) = "en") . ?river rdfs:label ?riverLabel . FILTER (LANG(?riverLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?continentLabel

column1: Rivers in Antarctica
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?river ?riverLabel ?location WHERE {   ?river wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q355304;          wdt:P30 wd:Q51.   OPTIONAL { ?river wdt:P625 ?location. } ?river rdfs:label ?riverLabel . FILTER (LANG(?riverLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Body of water with the most watercourses ending in it
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?mouth (COUNT(?watercourse) AS ?count) WHERE {   ?watercourse wdt:P403+ ?mouth. } GROUP BY ?mouth ORDER BY DESC(?count) LIMIT 10

column1: Bridges over rivers in Leipzig
column2: PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> SELECT ?bridge (SAMPLE(?bridgeLabel) AS ?bridgeLabel_)        ?watercourse (SAMPLE(?watercourseLabel) AS ?watercourseLabel_)        (SAMPLE(?loc) AS ?loc_) (SAMPLE(?pic) AS ?pic_)        (SAMPLE(?s) AS ?start) WHERE {   {     SELECT ?bridge ?watercourse WHERE {       ?bridge wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q12280;               wdt:P177 ?watercourse .       ?watercourse wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q355304 .     }   }   ?bridge wdt:P131+ wd:Q2079 .   OPTIONAL { ?bridge wdt:P625 ?loc. }   OPTIONAL { ?bridge wdt:P18 ?pic. }   OPTIONAL { ?bridge wdt:P571 ?s. }   ?bridge rdfs:label ?bridgeLabel. FILTER(LANG(?bridgeLabel)="en")   ?watercourse rdfs:label ?watercourseLabel. FILTER(LANG(?watercourseLabel)="en") } GROUP BY ?bridge ?watercourse

column1: Mountains, with coordinates, not located on Earth
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?name ?coord ?lat ?lon ?globe WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q8502 ;         p:P625 ?plholder1.   ?plholder1 psv:P625 ?plholder2 .   ?plholder2 wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat ;              wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon ;              wikibase:geoGlobe ?globe .   ?plholder1 ps:P625 ?coord .   FILTER ( ?globe != wd:Q2 ).   ?item rdfs:label ?name . FILTER(lang(?name) = "en") } ORDER BY ASC (?name)

column1: Highest mountains in the universe
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?subj ?label ?coord ?elev WHERE {    ?subj wdt:P2044 ?elev .  FILTER(?elev > 8000) .    ?subj wdt:P625 ?coord . }

column1: Mountains over 8000 elevation
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?subj ?label ?coord ?elev WHERE {    ?subj wdt:P2044 ?elev .  FILTER(?elev > 8000) .    ?subj wdt:P625 ?coord . }

column1: Italian mountains higher than 4000 m
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?coord ?elev ?picture WHERE {   ?item p:P2044/psn:P2044/wikibase:quantityAmount ?elev ;         wdt:P625 ?coord ;         wdt:P17 wd:Q38 ;         wdt:P18 ?picture .   FILTER(?elev > 4000). ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Metro stations in Paris
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?adjacent ?adjacentL ?coords WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q928830 ;         wdt:P81 wd:Q13224 ;         wdt:P625 ?coords .   OPTIONAL {     ?item p:P197 ?plholder1  . ?plholder1 ps:P197 ?adjacent . ?plholder1 pq:P5051 wd:Q585752 . ?plholder1 pq:P81 wd:Q13224 .     ?adjacent rdfs:label ?adjacentL . FILTER (lang(?adjacentL) = "en")   } ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?itemLabel

column1: How many states this US state borders
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?state ?stateLabel ?borders WHERE {   {     SELECT ?state (COUNT(?otherState) AS ?borders)     WHERE     {     ?state wdt:P31 wd:Q35657 .     ?otherState wdt:P47 ?state .     ?otherState wdt:P31 wd:Q35657 .     }     GROUP BY ?state   } ?state rdfs:label ?stateLabel . FILTER (LANG(?stateLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?borders)

column1: Places that are below 10 meters above sea level
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/> SELECT ?place ?location ?elev ?image WHERE {   ?place p:P2044/psv:P2044 ?placeElev.   ?placeElev wikibase:quantityAmount ?elev.   ?placeElev wikibase:quantityUnit ?unit.   FILTER ( ?elev < 10 ) .   FILTER ( ?unit = wd:Q11573 ) .   ?place wdt:P625 ?location.   OPTIONAL { ?place wdt:P18 ?image } }

column1: Globes used to represent coordinates
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> SELECT (COUNT(?v) AS ?c) ?globe WHERE {   ?v wikibase:geoGlobe ?globe } GROUP BY ?globe ORDER BY DESC(?c)

column1: Select French municipalities by INSEE code (select by identifier)
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?inseeCode WHERE {   ?item wdt:P374 ?inseeCode .    ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Map and list of municipalities in The Netherlands
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?muni ?muniLabel ?location WHERE {   ?muni p:P31 ?instanceOf;         wdt:P625 ?location.   ?instanceOf ps:P31 wd:Q2039348.   MINUS { ?muni wdt:P31 wd:Q7265977. }   MINUS { ?instanceOf pq:P582 ?endTime. } ?muni rdfs:label ?muniLabel . FILTER (LANG(?muniLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Emergency numbers by population using them
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?emergencyNumber ?emergencyNumberLabel ?tel ?population ?countries WHERE {  ?emergencyNumber wdt:P31 wd:Q694554 .   {SELECT ?emergencyNumber (COUNT(?state) AS ?countries) (SUM(?pop) AS ?population) WHERE {      ?state wdt:P2852 ?emergencyNumber .      OPTIONAL{?state wdt:P1082 ?pop} .      ?state wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q6256   } GROUP BY ?emergencyNumber } .   OPTIONAL{?emergencyNumber wdt:P1329 ?tel } ?emergencyNumber rdfs:label ?emergencyNumberLabel . FILTER (LANG(?emergencyNumberLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?population)

column1: German states, ordered by the number of company headquarters per million inhabitants
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT    ?state ?stateLabel    ?companies    ?population   WHERE {    { SELECT ?state (COUNT(?company) AS ?companies) WHERE {       {SELECT DISTINCT ?company ?state WHERE {          ?state wdt:P31 wd:Q1221156 .          ?company wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q4830453 .          ?company wdt:P159/wdt:P131* ?state .                 } }    } GROUP BY ?state  }     ?state wdt:P1082 ?population. ?state rdfs:label ?stateLabel . FILTER (LANG(?stateLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Popular names per birthplace
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?cid ?firstname (COUNT(?firstname) AS ?count) WHERE {   ?pid wdt:P19 wd:Q64.   ?pid wdt:P735 ?cid.   OPTIONAL {     ?cid rdfs:label ?firstname .     FILTER(LANG(?firstname) = "en")   } } GROUP BY ?cid ?firstname ORDER BY DESC(?count) ?firstname LIMIT 50

column1: Map of places mentioned in travel stories with text in French accessible online
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?ed ?edLabel ?auteurLabel ?dateCreation ?lieuLabel ?coord ?lien WHERE {   ?item wdt:P136 wd:Q1164267 .   ?item  wdt:P31 wd:Q47461344 .   OPTIONAL{     ?item wdt:P50 ?auteur .     ?auteur rdfs:label ?auteurLabel . FILTER (LANG(?auteurLabel) = "en") .   }   OPTIONAL{     ?item wdt:P571 ?dateCreation.   }   ?item  wdt:P840 ?lieu .   MINUS{ ?item wdt:P840 wd:Q933 }   ?lieu wdt:P625 ?coord .   {     ?item wdt:P953 ?lien .     ?item wdt:P407 wd:Q150   }UNION{     ?ed wdt:P629 ?item .     ?ed wdt:P953 ?lien .     ?ed wdt:P407 wd:Q150 .     ?ed rdfs:label ?edLabel . FILTER (LANG(?edLabel) = "en") .   } ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . ?lieu rdfs:label ?lieuLabel . FILTER (LANG(?lieuLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?dateCreation

column1: French communes with names ending in ac
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?coord WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q484170;         wdt:P17 wd:Q142;         rdfs:label ?itemLabel;         wdt:P625 ?coord;   FILTER (lang(?itemLabel) = "fr").       }

column1: Buildings in more than one country
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?count WHERE {   {     SELECT ?item (COUNT(DISTINCT ?country) AS ?count) WHERE {       ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q41176 .       ?item wdt:P17 ?country .            }     GROUP BY ?item   }   FILTER ( ?count > 1 ). ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?count)

column1: Streets named after a person
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?street ?streetLabel ?cityLabel ?personLabel WHERE {     ?street wdt:P31 wd:Q79007 .     ?street wdt:P17 wd:Q142 .     ?street wdt:P131 ?city .     ?street wdt:P138 ?person .     ?person wdt:P31 wd:Q5. ?city rdfs:label ?cityLabel . FILTER (LANG(?cityLabel) = "en") . ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel . FILTER (LANG(?personLabel) = "en") . ?street rdfs:label ?streetLabel . FILTER (LANG(?streetLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?city

column1: Streets in France without a city
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?street ?streetLabel WHERE {     ?street wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q79007 .     ?street wdt:P17 wd:Q142 .     MINUS { ?street wdt:P131 ?plholder1 } . ?street rdfs:label ?streetLabel . FILTER (LANG(?streetLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?streetLabel

column1: Ten largest islands in the world
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> SELECT DISTINCT ?island ?islandLabel ?islandImage WHERE {   ?island wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q23442.   OPTIONAL { ?island wdt:P18 ?islandImage. }   ?island p:P2046/psn:P2046/wikibase:quantityAmount ?islandArea. ?island rdfs:label ?islandLabel . FILTER (LANG(?islandLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?islandArea) LIMIT 10

column1: City gates in the Dutch province of Zeeland
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?town ?townLabel ?gate ?gateLabel WHERE {   ?muni wdt:P31 wd:Q2039348;         wdt:P131 wd:Q705.   ?gate wdt:P31 wd:Q82117;         wdt:P131 ?muni;         wdt:P276 ?town. ?gate rdfs:label ?gateLabel . FILTER (LANG(?gateLabel) = "en") . ?town rdfs:label ?townLabel . FILTER (LANG(?townLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Birthplaces of humans named Antoine
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?coord WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q5 .   ?item wdt:P735 wd:Q15235674.   ?item wdt:P19 ?place.   ?place wdt:P625 ?coord. ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Items with the most birth dates
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?person (COUNT(?date) AS ?dateC) WHERE {   ?person wdt:P569 ?date } GROUP BY ?person HAVING (?dateC > 2) ORDER BY DESC (?dateC) LIMIT 100

column1: Things/people with most children
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?parent ?parentLabel ?count WHERE {   {     SELECT ?parent (COUNT(?child) AS ?count)     WHERE     {       ?parent wdt:P40 ?child.     }     GROUP BY ?parent     ORDER BY DESC(?count)     LIMIT 10   } ?parent rdfs:label ?parentLabel . FILTER (LANG(?parentLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?count) LIMIT 10

column1: Population growth in Suriname from 1960 onward
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> SELECT ?year ?population WHERE {   wd:Q730 p:P1082 ?p .   ?p pq:P585 ?year ;      ps:P1082 ?population . } ORDER BY ?year

column1: Candidates for the Dutch general election in 2017
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?twitter ?politieke_partij ?politieke_partijLabel ?positie_op_lijst WHERE {   ?item p:P3602 ?node .     OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P2002 ?twitter }     ?node ps:P3602 wd:Q16061881 .     OPTIONAL { ?node pq:P1545 ?positie_op_lijst }     OPTIONAL { ?node pq:P1268 ?politieke_partij } ?politieke_partij rdfs:label ?politieke_partijLabel . FILTER (LANG(?politieke_partijLabel) = "en") . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Gender distribution in the candidates for the Dutch general election 2017
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?positie_op_lijst ?genderLabel ?politieke_partijLabel WHERE {   ?item p:P3602 ?node.   ?item wdt:P21 ?gender.   ?node ps:P3602 wd:Q16061881 .   ?node pq:P1545 ?positie_op_lijst.   ?node pq:P1268 ?politieke_partij. ?gender rdfs:label ?genderLabel . FILTER (LANG(?genderLabel) = "en") . ?politieke_partij rdfs:label ?politieke_partijLabel . FILTER (LANG(?politieke_partijLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Candidates for the Dutch general election 2017 living in Antwerp, Belgium
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?politieke_partij ?politieke_partijLabel WHERE {   ?item p:P3602 ?node.   ?item wdt:P551 wd:Q12892.   ?node ps:P3602 wd:Q16061881.   OPTIONAL { ?node pq:P1268 ?politieke_partij. } ?politieke_partij rdfs:label ?politieke_partijLabel . FILTER (LANG(?politieke_partijLabel) = "en") . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Candidates for the Dutch general election 2017 living abroad
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?coordinates WHERE {   ?item p:P3602 ?node.   ?item wdt:P551 ?residence .   ?residence wdt:P17 ?country ;              wdt:P625 ?coordinates .   ?node ps:P3602 wd:Q16061881.   FILTER (?country != wd:Q55). ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Occupations of candidates of the Dutch general election 2017
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?positie_op_lijst ?genderLabel ?occupationLabel ?politieke_partijLabel WHERE {   VALUES ?politieke_partij {wd:Q747910 wd:Q275441}   ?item p:P3602 ?node.   ?item wdt:P21 ?gender.   ?item wdt:P106 ?occupation.   ?node ps:P3602 wd:Q16061881.   ?node pq:P1545 ?positie_op_lijst.   ?node pq:P1268 ?politieke_partij. ?gender rdfs:label ?genderLabel . FILTER (LANG(?genderLabel) = "en") . ?occupation rdfs:label ?occupationLabel . FILTER (LANG(?occupationLabel) = "en") . ?politieke_partij rdfs:label ?politieke_partijLabel . FILTER (LANG(?politieke_partijLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Gender balance of members of Irish parliament
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?genderlabel (COUNT(?genderlabel) AS ?total) WHERE {    ?subj wdt:P39 wd:Q654291  .    ?subj wdt:P21 ?gender .    ?gender rdfs:label ?genderlabel . FILTER (lang(?genderlabel) = "en") .    ?subj rdfs:label ?label . FILTER (lang(?label) = "en") } GROUP BY ?genderlabel

column1: Assemblies by number of seats
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?title ?seats ?jurisdiction ?inception ?dissolution WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q1752346 .   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P1342 ?seats . }   OPTIONAL {     ?item wdt:P1001 ?j .     ?j rdfs:label ?jurisdiction . FILTER (lang(?jurisdiction) = "en") .   }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P571 ?inception . }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P576 ?dissolution . }   OPTIONAL { ?item rdfs:label ?title . FILTER (lang(?title) = "en") . } } ORDER BY DESC(?seats) ?title

column1: List of countries by age of the head of government
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?dob ?country ?countryLabel ?hgovernment ?hgovernmentLabel WHERE {    ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q3624078 .        ?country p:P6 ?statement .    ?statement ps:P6 ?hgovernment .    ?country wdt:P6 ?hgovernment .        ?hgovernment wdt:P569 ?dob .      ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel . FILTER (LANG(?countryLabel) = "en") . ?hgovernment rdfs:label ?hgovernmentLabel . FILTER (LANG(?hgovernmentLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?dob

column1: Number of ministers who are themselves children of a minister, per country
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?cc (COUNT(DISTINCT ?child) AS ?number) WHERE {   ?child wdt:P31 wd:Q5 ;          wdt:P39/wdt:P279* wd:Q83307 ;          wdt:P22|wdt:P25 ?plholder1 ;          wdt:P27/wdt:P901 ?cc .   ?plholder1 wdt:P39/wdt:P279* wd:Q83307 . } GROUP BY ?cc ORDER BY DESC(?number)

column1: Members of the French National Assembly born out of France
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?placeLabel ?countryLabel WHERE {   ?item wdt:P39 wd:Q3044918 .   ?item wdt:P19 ?place .   ?place wdt:P17 ?country .    ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel . FILTER (LANG(?countryLabel) = "en") . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . ?place rdfs:label ?placeLabel . FILTER (LANG(?placeLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?countryLabel ?itemLabel

column1: List of parliament buildings with pictures by country
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?building ?buildingLabel ?country ?countryLabel ?picture WHERE {   ?building wdt:P31 wd:Q7138926 .   ?building wdt:P18 ?picture .   OPTIONAL { ?building wdt:P17 ?country } . ?building rdfs:label ?buildingLabel . FILTER (LANG(?buildingLabel) = "en") . ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel . FILTER (LANG(?countryLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?countryLabel LIMIT 188

column1: Number of jurisdictions by driving side
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?sideLabel (COUNT(?jurisdiction) AS ?count) WHERE {   ?jurisdiction wdt:P1622 ?side. ?side rdfs:label ?sideLabel . FILTER (LANG(?sideLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?sideLabel ORDER BY ?sideLabel

column1: Timeline of mayors of Amsterdam, the Netherlands
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?mayor ?mayorLabel ?start ?end WHERE {   ?mayor p:P39 ?position.   ?position ps:P39 wd:Q13423495;             pq:P580 ?start;             pq:P582 ?end. ?mayor rdfs:label ?mayorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?mayorLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Current U.S. members of the Senate with district, party and date they assumed office
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?senator ?senatorLabel ?districtLabel ?partyLabel ?assumedOffice (sample(?image) AS ?image_) WHERE {   ?senator p:P39 ?posheld;            p:P102 ?partystatement.   ?partystatement ps:P102 ?party.   MINUS { ?partystatement pq:P582 ?partyEnd. }   MINUS { ?party wdt:P361 ?partOf. }   ?posheld ps:P39 wd:Q4416090;            pq:P768 ?district;            pq:P580 ?assumedOffice.   MINUS { ?posheld pq:P582 ?endTime. }   OPTIONAL { ?senator wdt:P18 ?image. } ?district rdfs:label ?districtLabel . FILTER (LANG(?districtLabel) = "en") . ?party rdfs:label ?partyLabel . FILTER (LANG(?partyLabel) = "en") . ?senator rdfs:label ?senatorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?senatorLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?senator ?senatorLabel ?districtLabel ?partyLabel ?assumedOffice ORDER BY ?senatorLabel

column1: Map of places of birth of dead economists, colour-coded by era
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?name ?birthplace ?dob ?coord WHERE { {?person wdt:P106 wd:Q188094} UNION {?person wdt:P101 wd:Q8134} ?person wdt:P570 ?dod;    wdt:P19 ?place . ?place wdt:P625 ?coord . OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:P569 ?dob }   ?person rdfs:label ?name . FILTER (lang(?name) = "en") ?place rdfs:label ?birthplace . FILTER (lang(?birthplace) = "en") } ORDER BY ?dob

column1: Distinct Billionaires
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?locationLabel ?item ?itemLabel (MAX(?worth_) AS ?worth) WHERE {   ?item wdt:P2218 ?worth_ .   ?item wdt:P19 ?location .   FILTER(?worth>1000000000).    ?location rdfs:label ?locationLabel . FILTER (LANG(?locationLabel) = "en") . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?locationLabel ?item ?itemLabel ORDER BY DESC(?worth)

column1: The number of existing translations for diseases in Wikidata
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?disease ?doid ?enLabel (COUNT(?language) AS ?languages) WHERE {    ?disease wdt:P699 ?doid ;              rdfs:label ?label ;              rdfs:label ?enLabel .     FILTER (lang(?enLabel) = "en")     BIND (?label AS ?language) } GROUP BY ?disease ?doid ?enLabel ORDER BY desc(?languages)

column1: A network of Drug-disease interactions on infectious diseases (Source: Disease Ontology, NDF-RT and ChEMBL)
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?disease ?diseaseLabel ?drug ?drugLabel WHERE {      ?disease wdt:P699 ?doid;            wdt:P279+ wd:Q18123741;            wdt:P2176 ?drug.   ?drug rdfs:label ?drugLabel.       FILTER(LANG(?drugLabel) = "en").   ?disease rdfs:label ?diseaseLabel.       FILTER(LANG(?diseaseLabel) = "en").             }

column1: The number of Wikidata items on Diseases and the percentage of those with a pointer to the Disease Ontology
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (COUNT(?disease) AS ?total) WHERE {   {?disease wdt:P31 wd:Q12136 }   UNION   {?disease wdt:P279 wd:Q12136 .}   OPTIONAL {     ?disease p:P699 ?statement.        } }

column1: Human genes updated this week
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?ncbi_gene ?date_modified WHERE {   ?item wdt:P351 ?ncbi_gene ;         wdt:P703 wd:Q15978631 .    ?x   schema:about ?item ;         schema:dateModified ?date_modified .   FILTER(?date_modified >= "2020-10-16T00:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime)   FILTER(?date_modified < "2020-10-23T00:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime) }

column1: Counts of gene-variant types sourced from the CIViC database
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT  ?variant_typeLabel (COUNT(?variant_typeLabel) AS ?counts) WHERE {   ?item wdt:P3329 ?civic_id ;           wdt:P31 ?variant_type . ?variant_type rdfs:label ?variant_typeLabel . FILTER (LANG(?variant_typeLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?variant_typeLabel ORDER BY ?counts

column1: Which variant of which gene predicts a positive prognosis in colorectal cancer
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?geneLabel ?variantLabel WHERE {   VALUES ?disease {wd:Q188874}     ?variant wdt:P3358 ?disease ;           wdt:P3433 ?gene . ?gene rdfs:label ?geneLabel . FILTER (LANG(?geneLabel) = "en") . ?variant rdfs:label ?variantLabel . FILTER (LANG(?variantLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Variants that are associated with renal cell carcinoma
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?civic_id ?item ?itemLabel WHERE {    VALUES ?property {                       wdt:P3356                       wdt:P3357                       wdt:P3358                       wdt:P3359                      }     ?item wdt:P3329 ?civic_id .     {?item  ?property wd:Q1164529.}     UNION     {     {?item p:P3354 ?o .      ?o pq:P2175 wd:Q1164529 .}     UNION     {?item p:P3354 ?o .      ?o pq:P2175 wd:Q1164529 .}     } ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: PubMed references in CIViCdb
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> SELECT DISTINCT  ?reference ?referenceLabel ?pmid WHERE {   ?item wdt:P3329 ?civicId ;           ?property  ?object .     ?object prov:wasDerivedFrom ?provenance .     ?provenance pr:P248 ?reference .     ?reference wdt:P31 wd:Q13442814 ;                wdt:P698 ?pmid . ?reference rdfs:label ?referenceLabel . FILTER (LANG(?referenceLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Variant counts by predictor type
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT  ?propertyLabel (COUNT(?prognostic_type) AS ?counts) WHERE {   VALUES ?prognostic_type {wdt:P3354 wdt:P3355 wdt:P3356 wdt:P3357 wdt:P3358 wdt:P3359}     ?item wdt:P3329 ?civic_id ;           ?prognostic_type ?prognostic_value .     ?property wikibase:directClaim ?prognostic_type . ?property rdfs:label ?propertyLabel . FILTER (LANG(?propertyLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?propertyLabel ?prognostic_type ORDER BY ?counts

column1: Get Wikidata - UniprotId mappings for homo sapiens
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?uniprotid ?tax_node WHERE {   ?item wdt:P352 ?uniprotid ;           wdt:P703 wd:Q15978631 . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Metabolites and the species where they are found in
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> SELECT ?compound ?compoundLabel ?speciesLabel ?sourceLabel ?doi ?wpid WHERE {   ?compound wdt:P31 wd:Q11173.   MINUS { ?compound wdt:P31 wd:Q8054. }   ?compound p:P703 ?statement.   ?statement rdf:type wikibase:BestRank.   ?statement ps:P703 ?species.   OPTIONAL {     ?statement prov:wasDerivedFrom/pr:P248 ?source.     OPTIONAL { ?source wdt:P2410 ?wpid. }     OPTIONAL { ?source wdt:P356 ?doi. }     ?source rdfs:label ?sourceLabel . FILTER (LANG(?sourceLabel) = "en") .   } ?compound rdfs:label ?compoundLabel . FILTER (LANG(?compoundLabel) = "en") . ?species rdfs:label ?speciesLabel . FILTER (LANG(?speciesLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ASC(?compound)

column1: All human pathways from Wikipathways
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?pathway ?pathwayLabel ?wpid WHERE {    ?pathway wdt:P2410 ?wpid ;             wdt:P703 wd:Q15978631 . ?pathway rdfs:label ?pathwayLabel . FILTER (LANG(?pathwayLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Ranking of most cited work in WikiPathways
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?citation ?citationLabel (COUNT(?pathway) AS ?times_cited) WHERE {   ?pathway wdt:P2410 ?WikiPathwaysID ;            wdt:P2860 ?citation . ?citation rdfs:label ?citationLabel . FILTER (LANG(?citationLabel) = "en") .   } GROUP BY ?pathway ?citation ?citationLabel

column1: Gene and metabolite counts per pathway
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?path ?genes ?metabolites ?pathway WHERE {   {SELECT DISTINCT ?path (COUNT(?pwPart) AS ?genes) WHERE {       ?path wdt:P2410 ?WikipathsID.       ?path wdt:P527 ?pwPart.       ?pwPart wdt:P31 wd:Q7187.     }     GROUP BY ?path   }   {SELECT DISTINCT ?path (COUNT(?pwPart) AS ?metabolites) WHERE {       ?path wdt:P2410 ?WikipathsID.       ?path wdt:P527 ?pwPart.       ?pwPart wdt:P31 wd:Q11173.     }     GROUP BY ?path   }   OPTIONAL { ?path rdfs:label ?pathway. } } ORDER BY DESC(?genes)

column1: Biological pathways with protein structures in the PDB database
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?pathway ?pathwayLabel ?WikiPathways ?Reactome (COUNT(DISTINCT ?protein) AS ?count) WHERE {   VALUES ?pathwayType { wd:Q4915012 wd:Q2996394 }   ?pathway wdt:P31 ?pathwayType .   { ?pathway wdt:P527/wdt:P688 ?protein . } UNION { ?pathway wdt:P527 ?protein . }   ?protein wdt:P638 ?PDBID .   OPTIONAL { ?pathway wdt:P2410 ?WikiPathways }   OPTIONAL { ?pathway wdt:P3937 ?Reactome } ?pathway rdfs:label ?pathwayLabel . FILTER (LANG(?pathwayLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?pathway ?pathwayLabel ?WikiPathways ?Reactome   ORDER BY DESC(?count)

column1: Get known variants reported in CIViC database (Q27612411) of genes reported in a Wikipathways pathway: Bladder Cancer (Q30230812)
column2: PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?pathway ?pathwayLabel ?pwpart ?pwpartLabel ?variant ?variantLabel ?disease ?diseaseLabel WHERE {   VALUES ?predictor {p:P3354 p:P3355 p:P3356 p:P3357 p:P3358 p:P3359}   VALUES ?wpID {"WP2828"}   ?pathway wdt:P2410 ?wpID ;            wdt:P527 ?pwpart .   ?disease wdt:P279+ wd:Q504775 .   ?variant wdt:P3329 ?civicID ;            ?predictor ?node ;            wdt:P3433 ?pwpart .   ?node ?predictorStatement ?disease .   ?disease rdfs:label ?diseaseLabel . FILTER(LANG(?diseaseLabel)="en")   ?pathway rdfs:label ?pathwayLabel . FILTER(LANG(?pathwayLabel)="en")   ?pwpart rdfs:label ?pwpartLabel . FILTER(LANG(?pwpartLabel)="en")   ?variant rdfs:label ?variantLabel . FILTER(LANG(?variantLabel)="en") }

column1: Find drugs for cancers that target genes related to cell proliferation
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?drugLabel ?geneLabel ?biological_processLabel ?diseaseLabel WHERE {   ?drug wdt:P129 ?gene_product .   ?gene wdt:P688 ?gene_product .   ?disease   wdt:P2293 ?gene .   ?disease wdt:P279+  wd:Q12078 .   ?gene_product wdt:P682 ?biological_process .    ?biological_process wdt:P361/wdt:P279* wd:Q189101 . ?disease rdfs:label ?diseaseLabel . FILTER (LANG(?diseaseLabel) = "en") . ?gene rdfs:label ?geneLabel . FILTER (LANG(?geneLabel) = "en") . ?biological_process rdfs:label ?biological_processLabel . FILTER (LANG(?biological_processLabel) = "en") . ?drug rdfs:label ?drugLabel . FILTER (LANG(?drugLabel) = "en") . } LIMIT 1000

column1: Parent taxons of Blue Whale
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?pic ?linkTo WHERE {   wd:Q42196 wdt:P171+ ?item .   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P171 ?linkTo }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P18 ?pic } ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Mosquito species
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?item ?taxonname WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q16521 ;         wdt:P105 wd:Q7432 ;         wdt:P171+ wd:Q7367 ;         wdt:P225 ?taxonname . }

column1: Taxons and what they are named after
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?taxon ?eponym ?taxonName ?eponymLabel WHERE {   ?taxon wdt:P31 wd:Q16521;          wdt:P225 ?taxonName;          wdt:P138 ?eponym. ?eponym rdfs:label ?eponymLabel . FILTER (LANG(?eponymLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?eponym

column1: Biologists with Twitter accounts
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?personLabel ?twitterName ?pic WHERE {   ?person wdt:P2002 ?twitterName ;     wdt:P106 ?occupation .   OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:P18 ?pic . }   ?occupation wdt:P279+ wd:Q864503 . ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel . FILTER (LANG(?personLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Cell lines with names that could also be URLs (Internet of Cell Lines).
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?cell_line ?cell_line_name ?tld ?tld_name ?url WHERE {   {     SELECT ?cell_line ?cell_line_name WHERE {       ?cell_line wdt:P31 wd:Q21014462;                  rdfs:label ?cell_line_name.       FILTER(LANG(?cell_line_name) = "en").     }   }   ?tld wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q14296;        rdfs:label ?tld_name.   FILTER(LANG(?tld_name) = "en").       }  LIMIT 10000000

column1: List of pharmaceutical drugs with picture
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?moleculeLabel ?formule ?picture ?molecule WHERE {   ?molecule  wdt:P31 wd:Q12140   ; wdt:P274 ?formule   ; wdt:P117 ?picture. ?molecule rdfs:label ?moleculeLabel . FILTER (LANG(?moleculeLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?moleculeLabel

column1: Organisms that are located in the female urogential tract and that have a gene with product indole
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?organism_name WHERE {   ?organism_item wdt:P2974 wd:Q5880;   rdfs:label ?organism_name .   ?gene wdt:P703 ?organism_item;   wdt:P1056 wd:Q319541 .   FILTER (LANG(?organism_name) = "en") . }

column1: List of computer files formats
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?idExtension ?extension ?mediaType ?idExtensionLabel WHERE {   ?idExtension wdt:P31 wd:Q235557   ; wdt:P1195 ?extension .   OPTIONAL { ?idExtension wdt:P1163 ?mediaType } ?idExtension rdfs:label ?idExtensionLabel . FILTER (LANG(?idExtensionLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?extension ?mediaType

column1: List of W3C standards
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?standard ?standardLabel ?website WHERE {         ?standard wdt:P1462 wd:Q37033 .         OPTIONAL{ ?standard wdt:P856 ?website } ?standard rdfs:label ?standardLabel . FILTER (LANG(?standardLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?standardLabel

column1: Oldest software
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?software ?softwareLabel ?date WHERE {   ?software wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q7397.   OPTIONAL { ?software wdt:P571 ?date. }   OPTIONAL { ?software p:P348/pq:P577 ?date. }    ?software rdfs:label ?softwareLabel . FILTER (LANG(?softwareLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?date LIMIT 10

column1: Universities of main programming language authors
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?lang ?langLabel ?human ?humanLabel ?educatedat ?educatedatLabel ?coords WHERE {   ?lang wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q9143 .   ?human wdt:P31 wd:Q5 .   { ?lang wdt:P287 ?human } UNION {{ ?lang wdt:P170 ?human } UNION { ?lang wdt:P178 ?human }} .   ?human wdt:P69 ?educatedat .   ?educatedat wdt:P625 ?coords . ?human rdfs:label ?humanLabel . FILTER (LANG(?humanLabel) = "en") . ?educatedat rdfs:label ?educatedatLabel . FILTER (LANG(?educatedatLabel) = "en") . ?lang rdfs:label ?langLabel . FILTER (LANG(?langLabel) = "en") . } LIMIT 100

column1: Websites with OpenAPI endpoints
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?database ?databaseLabel ?license ?licenseLabel ?value WHERE {   ?wds pq:P31 wd:Q27075870.   ?database ?p ?wds .   ?database wdt:P275 ?license .   ?wds ?v ?value.   ?wdP wikibase:statementProperty ?v.   ?wdP wikibase:claim ?p. ?database rdfs:label ?databaseLabel . FILTER (LANG(?databaseLabel) = "en") . ?license rdfs:label ?licenseLabel . FILTER (LANG(?licenseLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ASC(?databaseLabel)

column1: E-Readers that support the mobipocket file format
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?ereader ?ereaderLabel WHERE {   ?ereader wdt:P31  wd:Q726235 .   ?ereader wdt:P1072 wd:Q1941622 . ?ereader rdfs:label ?ereaderLabel . FILTER (LANG(?ereaderLabel) = "en") .   }

column1: Software applications ranked in descending order by the number of writable file formats
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?app ?appLabel (COUNT(?format) AS ?count) WHERE {   ?app p:P31/ps:P31/wdt:P279 wd:Q7397 .   ?app wdt:P1072 ?format . ?app rdfs:label ?appLabel . FILTER (LANG(?appLabel) = "en") .   } GROUP BY ?app ?appLabel ORDER BY DESC(?count)

column1: Return a bubble chart of mediatypes by count of file formats
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT DISTINCT ?mediaType (COUNT (?ff) AS ?count) WHERE {   ?ff wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q235557.   ?ff wdt:P1163 ?mediaType. } GROUP BY ?mediaType ORDER BY DESC (?count)

column1: Erdos Numbers and images of people who have oral histories in the Computer History Museum's collection
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT  ?personLabel  ?image ?Erdos WHERE {   ?person wdt:P485 wd:Q964035 .   ?person wdt:P18 ?image .   ?person wdt:P2021 ?Erdos. ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel . FILTER (LANG(?personLabel) = "en") .   }

column1: Chemical elements and their properties
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?elementLabel ?_boiling_point ?_melting_point ?_electronegativity ?_density ?_mass WHERE {   ?element wdt:P31 wd:Q11344.   ?element wdt:P2102 ?_boiling_point.   ?element wdt:P2101 ?_melting_point.   ?element wdt:P1108 ?_electronegativity.   ?element wdt:P2054 ?_density.   ?element wdt:P2067 ?_mass. ?element rdfs:label ?elementLabel . FILTER (LANG(?elementLabel) = "en") . } LIMIT 100

column1: Chemical elements and their isotopes by number of neutrons (min/max)
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?element (SAMPLE(?symbol_) AS ?symbol) (SAMPLE(?protons_) AS ?protons) (MIN(?neutrons) AS ?minNeutrons) (MAX(?neutrons) AS ?maxNeutrons) WHERE {   ?element wdt:P31 wd:Q11344;            wdt:P1086 ?protons_;            wdt:P246 ?symbol_.   ?isotope wdt:P279 ?element;            wdt:P1148 ?neutrons. } GROUP BY ?element ORDER BY ?protons

column1: Colors of chemical compounds
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?rgb ?colorLabel (COUNT(?compound) AS ?count) WHERE {   ?compound wdt:P31 wd:Q11173;             wdt:P462 ?color.   OPTIONAL { ?color wdt:P465 ?rgb. }    ?color rdfs:label ?colorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?colorLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?rgb ?colorLabel

column1: All pKa data in Wikidata and the source titles
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> SELECT ?compound ?compoundLabel ?pKa ?source ?sourceLabel ?doi WHERE {   ?compound wdt:P31 wd:Q11173 ; p:P1117 ?statement .   ?statement rdf:type wikibase:BestRank ;     ps:P1117 ?pKa .   OPTIONAL {     ?statement prov:wasDerivedFrom/pr:P248 ?source .     ?source rdfs:label ?sourceLabel . FILTER (LANG(?sourceLabel) = "en") .     OPTIONAL { ?source wdt:P356 ?doi . }   } ?compound rdfs:label ?compoundLabel . FILTER (LANG(?compoundLabel) = "en") . }

column1: All CAS registry numbers in Wikidata
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?compound ?compoundLabel ?cas WHERE {   ?compound wdt:P231 ?cas . ?compound rdfs:label ?compoundLabel . FILTER (LANG(?compoundLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Chemical compounds in Wikidata sharing the same CAS registry number
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?cas ?compound1 ?compound1Label ?compound2 ?compound2Label WHERE {   ?compound1 wdt:P231 ?cas .   ?compound2 wdt:P231 ?cas .   FILTER (?compound1 != ?compound2). ?compound1 rdfs:label ?compound1Label . FILTER (LANG(?compound1Label) = "en") . ?compound2 rdfs:label ?compound2Label . FILTER (LANG(?compound2Label) = "en") . }

column1: The number of Chemical compounds in Wikidata sharing the same CAS registry number
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?cas ?items WHERE {   {SELECT DISTINCT ?cas (COUNT(?compound) AS ?items) WHERE {       ?compound wdt:P231 ?cas .   }     GROUP BY ?cas }     FILTER (?items >1) } ORDER BY desc(?items)

column1: Awarded Chemistry Nobel Prizes
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?when ?pic WHERE {   ?item p:P166 ?awardStat .   ?awardStat ps:P166 wd:Q44585 .   ?awardStat pq:P585 ?when . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P18 ?pic } }

column1: Images of organic acids
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?compound ?compoundLabel ?image WHERE {   ?compound wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q421948 ;             wdt:P18|wdt:P117 ?image . ?compound rdfs:label ?compoundLabel . FILTER (LANG(?compoundLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Boiling points of alkanes
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/> SELECT DISTINCT ?comp ?compLabel ?formula ?bp ?bpUnit ?bpUnitLabel WHERE {   ?comp wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q41581 ;         wdt:P274 ?formula ;         p:P2102 ?plholder1  . ?plholder1 ps:P2102 ?bp ;            psv:P2102/wikibase:quantityUnit ?bpUnit . ?comp rdfs:label ?compLabel . FILTER (LANG(?compLabel) = "en") . ?bpUnit rdfs:label ?bpUnitLabel . FILTER (LANG(?bpUnitLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?bpUnit) ASC(?bp)

column1: Solubilities of chemicals
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX pqv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/value/> PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> SELECT DISTINCT ?chemical ?chemicalLabel ?value ?units ?unitsLabel ?solvent ?solventLabel ?temperature ?temperatureUnit ?temperatureUnitLabel ?source ?sourceLabel ?doi WHERE {   {     SELECT DISTINCT ?chemical ?value ?units ?source ?doi ?solvent ?temperature ?temperatureUnit WHERE {       ?property wikibase:claim ?propp ;                 wikibase:statementValue ?proppsv ;                 wdt:P1629 wd:Q170731 ;                 wdt:P31 wd:Q21077852 .       ?statement rdf:type wikibase:BestRank ;                  ?proppsv ?plholder1  .       ?plholder1 wikibase:quantityAmount ?value .       ?plholder1 wikibase:quantityUnit ?units .       OPTIONAL {         ?statement prov:wasDerivedFrom/pr:P248 ?source .         OPTIONAL { ?source wdt:P356 ?doi . }         ?source rdfs:label ?sourceLabel . FILTER (LANG(?sourceLabel) = "en") .       }       ?chemical ?propp ?statement .       OPTIONAL {         ?statement pqv:P2076 ?temperatureNode .         ?temperatureNode wikibase:quantityAmount ?temperature ;                          wikibase:quantityUnit ?temperatureUnit .         ?temperatureUnit rdfs:label ?temperatureUnitLabel . FILTER (LANG(?temperatureUnitLabel) = "en") .       }       OPTIONAL {         wd:P2178 wikibase:qualifier ?qualifierS .         ?qualifierS rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .         ?statement ?qualifierS ?solvent .         ?solvent rdfs:label ?solventLabel . FILTER (LANG(?solventLabel) = "en") .       }     }     GROUP BY ?chemical ?value ?units ?temperature ?temperatureUnit ?solvent ?source ?doi   } ?chemical rdfs:label ?chemicalLabel . FILTER (LANG(?chemicalLabel) = "en") . ?units rdfs:label ?unitsLabel . FILTER (LANG(?unitsLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Who discovered the most asteroids?
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?discoverer ?name (COUNT(?asteroid) AS ?count) WHERE {    ?asteroid wdt:P31 wd:Q3863 .    ?asteroid wdt:P61 ?discoverer .    ?discoverer rdfs:label ?name . FILTER (LANG(?name) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?discoverer ?name ORDER BY DESC(?count) LIMIT 20

column1: Who discovered the most planets? (with list)
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT    ?discoverer ?discovererLabel    (COUNT(DISTINCT ?planet) AS ?count)    (GROUP_CONCAT(?planetLabel; SEPARATOR=", ") AS ?planets) WHERE {    ?ppart wdt:P279+ wd:Q634 .    ?planet wdt:P31 ?ppart .    ?planet wdt:P61 ?discoverer . ?planet rdfs:label ?planetLabel . FILTER (LANG(?planetLabel) = "en") . ?discoverer rdfs:label ?discovererLabel . FILTER (LANG(?discovererLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?discoverer ?discovererLabel ORDER BY DESC(?count)

column1: List of space probes with pictures
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?spaceProbeLabel ?date ?picture WHERE {   ?spaceProbe wdt:P31 wd:Q26529;         wdt:P18 ?picture;         wdt:P619 ?date . ?spaceProbe rdfs:label ?spaceProbeLabel . FILTER (LANG(?spaceProbeLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?date LIMIT 88

column1: Birthplaces of astronauts
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?astronaut ?astronautLabel ?image ?birthdate ?birthplace ?coord WHERE {   ?astronaut ?x1 wd:Q11631;   wdt:P18 ?image;   wdt:P569 ?birthdate;   wdt:P19 ?birthplace.   ?birthplace wdt:P625 ?coord. ?astronaut rdfs:label ?astronautLabel . FILTER (LANG(?astronautLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?birthdate)

column1: (Artist) Images of Exoplanets
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?exoplanet ?exoplanetLabel ?image WHERE {   ?exoplanet wdt:P31 wd:Q44559 ;              wdt:P18 ?image . ?exoplanet rdfs:label ?exoplanetLabel . FILTER (LANG(?exoplanetLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Number of scientists per gender
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?gender (COUNT(DISTINCT ?human) AS ?number) WHERE {   ?human wdt:P31 wd:Q5   ; wdt:P21 ?gender   ; wdt:P106/wdt:P279* wd:Q901 . } GROUP BY ?gender LIMIT 10

column1: Most eponymous mathematicians
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?eponym ?eponymLabel ?count ?sample ?sampleLabel WHERE {   {   SELECT ?eponym (COUNT(?item) AS ?count) (SAMPLE(?item) AS ?sample)   WHERE   {     ?item wdt:P138 ?eponym.     ?eponym wdt:P106 wd:Q170790.   }   GROUP BY ?eponym   } ?eponym rdfs:label ?eponymLabel . FILTER (LANG(?eponymLabel) = "en") . ?sample rdfs:label ?sampleLabel . FILTER (LANG(?sampleLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?count)

column1: Authors of scientific articles by occupation
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?occupationLabel (COUNT(DISTINCT ?author) AS ?count) WHERE {         ?object wdt:P31 wd:Q13442814         ; wdt:P50 ?author .         ?author wdt:P106 ?occupation . ?occupation rdfs:label ?occupationLabel . FILTER (LANG(?occupationLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?occupationLabel ORDER BY DESC(?count)

column1: Authors of scientific articles who received a Nobel prize
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?person ?personLabel ?_image ?award ?awardLabel WHERE {   ?person wdt:P166 ?award ;           wdt:P31 wd:Q5 .   ?award wdt:P361 wd:Q7191 .   ?item wdt:P50 ?person ;         wdt:P31 wd:Q13442814 . ?award rdfs:label ?awardLabel . FILTER (LANG(?awardLabel) = "en") . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel . FILTER (LANG(?personLabel) = "en") . OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:P18 ?_image. } }

column1: Using VALUES for extracting scientific articles of specific authors
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?entity ?entityLabel ?authorLabel WHERE {   VALUES ?author {wd:Q18016466}   ?entity wdt:P31 wd:Q13442814.   ?entity wdt:P50 ?author. ?author rdfs:label ?authorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?authorLabel) = "en") . ?entity rdfs:label ?entityLabel . FILTER (LANG(?entityLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Female scientists with most number of sitelinks (but not English Wikipedia)
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?linkcount WHERE {     ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q5 .     ?item wdt:P21 wd:Q6581072 .     ?item wdt:P106 wd:Q901 .     ?item ^schema:about/wikibase:sitelinks ?linkcount .   FILTER (?linkcount >= 1) .    ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel ?linkcount ORDER BY DESC(?linkcount)

column1: Inventors killed by their own invention
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?inventor ?inventorLabel ?gadget ?gadgetLabel WHERE {   ?inventor wdt:P157 ?gadget.   ?gadget wdt:P61 ?inventor. ?gadget rdfs:label ?gadgetLabel . FILTER (LANG(?gadgetLabel) = "en") . ?inventor rdfs:label ?inventorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?inventorLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Most cited female authors
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?author ?authorLabel (COUNT(?publication) AS ?count) WHERE {     ?author wdt:P21 wd:Q6581072.     ?item wdt:P2860 ?publication .     ?publication wdt:P50 ?author . ?author rdfs:label ?authorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?authorLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?author ?authorLabel ORDER BY DESC(?count)

column1: Scientists who have worked together but whose Erdos numbers donâ€™t reflect that
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?paper ?author1 ?author2 ?title ?paperLabel ?author1Label ?erdos1 ?author2Label ?erdos2 WHERE {   ?paper wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q13442814;            wdt:P50 ?author1;            wdt:P50 ?author2.   OPTIONAL { ?paper wdt:P1476 ?title. }   ?author1 wdt:P2021 ?erdos1.   ?author2 wdt:P2021 ?erdos2.   BIND(?erdos2 - ?erdos1 AS ?distance).   FILTER(?distance > 1). ?author1 rdfs:label ?author1Label . FILTER (LANG(?author1Label) = "en") . ?author2 rdfs:label ?author2Label . FILTER (LANG(?author2Label) = "en") . ?paper rdfs:label ?paperLabel . FILTER (LANG(?paperLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?author1Label ?author2Label

column1: Map of institutions where Canadian citizens got their PhD
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?institution ?institutionLabel ?academics ?academicsLabel ?degree ?degreeLabel ?geoloc  ?image WHERE {   ?academics wdt:P31 wd:Q5 ;              wdt:P27 wd:Q16 ;              p:P69 ?statement .   OPTIONAL { ?academics wdt:P18 ?image }.   ?statement ps:P69 ?institution .   ?institution wdt:P625 ?geoloc .   ?statement pq:P512 ?degree .   ?degree wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q849697 . ?academics rdfs:label ?academicsLabel . FILTER (LANG(?academicsLabel) = "en") . ?degree rdfs:label ?degreeLabel . FILTER (LANG(?degreeLabel) = "en") . ?institution rdfs:label ?institutionLabel . FILTER (LANG(?institutionLabel) = "en") . }

column1: PMID-DOI mappings
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT DISTINCT ?pmid ?doi WHERE {   ?item wdt:P698 ?pmid ;               wdt:P356 ?doi . }

column1: number of statements backed by a reference with a DOI
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/> PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> SELECT (COUNT (?statement) AS ?statements) WHERE {   ?statement prov:wasDerivedFrom/pr:P248/wdt:P356 ?doi .   ?entry ?p ?statement . }

column1: Statements originating from a specific DOI
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> SELECT ?entryRes ?entry ?statement WHERE {   ?statement prov:wasDerivedFrom/pr:P248/wdt:P356 "10.1021/JA01577A030" .   ?entryRes ?p ?statement ;             rdfs:label ?entry .   FILTER(lang(?entry) = "en") }

column1: Translations of the Disease Ontology term DOID:399 (Tuberculosis)
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?English ?label WHERE {    ?disease wdt:P699 "DOID:399";              rdfs:label ?English;              rdfs:label ?label .                     FILTER (LANG(?English)="en")     }

column1: Library and Information Science journals
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?journal ?name WHERE {     ?journal wdt:P31 wd:Q5633421 .             { ?journal wdt:P921 wd:Q199655 }       UNION {{ ?journal wdt:P921 wd:Q16387 }       UNION { ?journal wdt:P921 wd:Q13420675 }}     ?journal rdfs:label ?name . FILTER (LANG(?name) = "en") . }

column1: Most popular subjects of scientific articles
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT (COUNT(?work) AS ?count) ?subject ?subjectLabel WHERE {   ?work wdt:P31 wd:Q13442814;         wdt:P921 ?subject . ?subject rdfs:label ?subjectLabel . FILTER (LANG(?subjectLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?subject ?subjectLabel ORDER BY desc(?count) LIMIT 200

column1: Scientific journals with editors on Twitter
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?journal ?journalLabel ?editor ?editorLabel ?twitter ?ex_publisher ?ex_publisherLabel WHERE {   {     SELECT ?journal ?editor ?twitter (SAMPLE(?publisher) AS ?ex_publisher) (SAMPLE(?publisherLabel) AS ?ex_publisherLabel) WHERE {       ?journal wdt:P31 wd:Q5633421 ; wdt:P98 ?editor .       OPTIONAL { ?journal wdt:P123 ?publisher . ?publisher rdfs:label ?publisherLabel . FILTER(lang(?publisherLabel) = "en") }       ?editor wdt:P2002 ?twitter .     } GROUP BY ?journal ?editor ?twitter   }   ?journal rdfs:label ?journalLabel . FILTER(lang(?journalLabel) = "en")   ?editor rdfs:label ?editorLabel . FILTER(lang(?editorLabel) = "en") } ORDER BY ?journalLabel

column1: Mathematical proofs
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?proof ?proofLabel WHERE {   ?proof wdt:P31 wd:Q11538. ?proof rdfs:label ?proofLabel . FILTER (LANG(?proofLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Timeline of death of mathematicans and their theorems
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT   ?genderLabel   ?theorem   ?theoremLabel   ?nameLabel   ?death   ?formula WHERE { ?gender rdfs:label ?genderLabel . FILTER (LANG(?genderLabel) = "en") . ?name rdfs:label ?nameLabel . FILTER (LANG(?nameLabel) = "en") . ?theorem rdfs:label ?theoremLabel . FILTER (LANG(?theoremLabel) = "en") .   ?theorem wdt:P31  wd:Q65943;            wdt:P138 ?name.   ?name    wdt:P570 ?death;            wdt:P21  ?gender .   ?theorem wdt:P2534 ?formula. } ORDER BY DESC(?death) LIMIT 100

column1: Databases listed in Wikidata and if available applicable licenses
