column1: List of actors with pictures with year of birth and/or death
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?human ?humanLabel ?yob ?yod ?picture WHERE {   ?human wdt:P31 wd:Q5   ; wdt:P106 wd:Q33999 .   ?human wdt:P18 ?picture .   OPTIONAL { ?human wdt:P569 ?dob . ?human wdt:P570 ?dod }.       ?human rdfs:label ?humanLabel . FILTER (LANG(?humanLabel) = "en") . } LIMIT 88

column1: Actors who played the same role more than 40 years apart
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?actor ?actorLabel ?characterLabel ?movie1Label ?movie2Label WHERE {   ?movie1 p:P161 ?plholder1 .   ?plholder1 ps:P161 ?actor;              pq:P453 ?character.   ?movie1 wdt:P577 ?movie1Publication.   ?movie2 p:P161 ?plholder2 .   ?plholder2 ps:P161 ?actor;              pq:P453 ?character .   ?movie2 wdt:P577 ?movie2Publication.   MINUS{?movie1 wdt:P31/wdt:P279? wd:Q24856}    MINUS{?movie2 wdt:P31/wdt:P279? wd:Q24856}    FILTER(?character != wd:Q18086706).   FILTER(?movie1Publication < ?movie2Publication)   ?actor rdfs:label ?actorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?actorLabel) = "en") .   ?character rdfs:label ?characterLabel . FILTER (LANG(?characterLabel) = "en") .   ?movie1 rdfs:label ?movie1Label . FILTER (LANG(?movie1Label) = "en") .   ?movie2 rdfs:label ?movie2Label . FILTER (LANG(?movie2Label) = "en") . }

column1: Authors, writers and poets ranked by sitelink and also includes "country of citizenship"
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> SELECT DISTINCT ?writer ?place ?linkcount WHERE {   {?s wdt:P106 wd:Q36180 .} UNION {{ ?s wdt:P106 wd:Q482980 . } UNION { ?s wdt:P106 wd:Q49757 . }}   ?s wdt:P27 ?pl .   ?s ^schema:about/wikibase:sitelinks ?linkcount .   OPTIONAL {      ?s rdfs:label ?writer . FILTER (lang(?writer) = "en").    }     OPTIONAL {      ?pl rdfs:label ?place . FILTER (lang(?place) = "en").    } } GROUP BY ?place ?writer ?linkcount HAVING (?linkcount > 10) ORDER BY DESC(?linkcount)

column1: Birth places of German poets
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?subj ?subjLabel ?place ?placeLabel ?coord ?birthyear WHERE {    ?subj wdt:P106 wd:Q49757 .    ?subj wdt:P19 ?place .    ?place wdt:P17 wd:Q183 .    ?place wdt:P625 ?coord .    OPTIONAL { ?subj wdt:P569 ?dob }     ?place rdfs:label ?placeLabel . FILTER (LANG(?placeLabel) = "en") . ?subj rdfs:label ?subjLabel . FILTER (LANG(?subjLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Books or literary works published before 1830 with place of publication or narrative location coordinates
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?label ?coord ?place WHERE {   VALUES ?type {wd:Q571 wd:Q7725634}   ?item wdt:P31 ?type .   ?item wdt:P577 ?date .    ?item rdfs:label ?label . FILTER (lang(?label) = "en")   OPTIONAL {     ?item (wdt:P291|wdt:P840) ?place .     ?place wdt:P625 ?coord   } }

column1: Books by a given Author including genres and year of first publication
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?book ?bookLabel ?authorLabel (GROUP_CONCAT(?genre_label) AS ?genres) (MIN(?publicationDate) AS ?firstPublication) WHERE {   ?author rdfs:label "Ernest Hemingway"@en .   ?book wdt:P50 ?author .   OPTIONAL {     ?book wdt:P136 ?genre .     ?genre rdfs:label ?genre_label . FILTER (lang(?genre_label) = "en").   }   OPTIONAL {     ?book wdt:P577 ?publicationDate .     ?book rdfs:label ?bookLabel . FILTER (LANG(?bookLabel) = "en") .   } ?author rdfs:label ?authorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?authorLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?book ?bookLabel ?authorLabel

column1: Text by author containing case-insensitive title with optional cover image
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?authorLabel ?itemLabel ?image WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q234460.   ?author ?label 'Bram Stoker'.   ?item wdt:P50 ?author.   ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel.      OPTIONAL {?item wdt:P18 ?image.} ?author rdfs:label ?authorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?authorLabel) = "en") . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . } LIMIT 50

column1: Literary works by label count
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?s ?desc (COUNT(DISTINCT ?label) AS ?labelcount) WHERE {   ?s wdt:P31 wd:Q7725634 .   ?s rdfs:label ?label .   OPTIONAL {      ?s rdfs:label ?desc . FILTER (lang(?desc) = "en").    }  } GROUP BY ?s ?desc ORDER BY DESC(?labelcount)

column1: All subclasses of "Literary Work"
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?s ?desc WHERE {   ?s wdt:P279 wd:Q7725634 .   OPTIONAL {      ?s rdfs:label ?desc . FILTER (lang(?desc) = "en").    }  }

column1: Epic poems by label count
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?s ?desc (COUNT(DISTINCT ?label) AS ?labelcount) WHERE {   ?s wdt:P31 wd:Q37484 .   ?s rdfs:label ?label .   OPTIONAL {      ?s rdfs:label ?desc . FILTER (lang(?desc) = "en").    }  } GROUP BY ?s ?desc ORDER BY DESC(?labelcount)

column1: Epic poems by sitelink count
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> SELECT ?s ?desc ?linkcount WHERE {   ?s wdt:P31 wd:Q37484 .   ?s ^schema:about/wikibase:sitelinks ?linkcount .   OPTIONAL {      ?s rdfs:label ?desc . FILTER (lang(?desc) = "en").    }  } GROUP BY ?s ?desc ?linkcount ORDER BY DESC(?linkcount)

column1: Instance of Book by sitelink count
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> SELECT ?s ?desc ?linkcount WHERE {   ?s wdt:P31 wd:Q571 .   ?s ^schema:about/wikibase:sitelinks ?linkcount .   OPTIONAL {      ?s rdfs:label ?desc . FILTER (lang(?desc) = "en").    }  } GROUP BY ?s ?desc ?linkcount ORDER BY DESC(?linkcount)

column1: Poets and monarchs
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?poetLabel ?image ?yob ?yod ?start ?end ?monarchLabel WHERE {   ?poet p:P39 ?positionStat.   ?positionStat ps:P39 wd:Q877838;                 pq:P580 ?start;                 pq:P748 ?monarch.   OPTIONAL {     ?positionStat pq:P582 ?end.   }   OPTIONAL {     ?poet wdt:P18 ?image;           wdt:P569 ?dob;           wdt:P570 ?dod.   }       ?monarch rdfs:label ?monarchLabel . FILTER (LANG(?monarchLabel) = "en") . ?poet rdfs:label ?poetLabel . FILTER (LANG(?poetLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?start DESC(?monarchLabel)

column1: List of digital libraries in the world
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?website WHERE { ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q212805 . OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P856 ?website } MINUS { ?item wdt:P576 ?x } ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?itemLabel

column1: Map of Libraries in Canada
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?library ?libraryLabel ?coords WHERE {   ?library wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q7075 .   ?library wdt:P17 wd:Q16 .   ?library wdt:P625 ?coords .   ?library rdfs:label ?libraryLabel . FILTER (LANG(?libraryLabel) = "en") . } LIMIT 100

column1: List of authors unsuccessfully nominated for Nobel prize in literature
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?nominee ?nomineeLabel (SAMPLE(?citizenshipLabel) AS ?country) (COUNT(DISTINCT ?time) AS ?timesNominated) WHERE {     ?nominee p:P1411 ?plholder1 .     ?plholder1 ps:P1411 wd:Q37922;                pq:P585 ?time .          OPTIONAL {       ?nominee wdt:P27 ?plholder2 .       ?plholder2 rdfs:label ?citizenshipLabel .       FILTER (lang(?citizenshipLabel) = "en") .     }      ?nominee rdfs:label ?nomineeLabel . FILTER (LANG(?nomineeLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?nominee ?nomineeLabel ORDER BY DESC(?timesNominated) ?nomineeLabel

column1: Authors whose works enter the public domain in 2017 (died in 1946)
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT DISTINCT ?item WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q5 ;   wdt:P106/wdt:P279* wd:Q482980 .   ?item wdt:P570 ?time0 .    }

column1: Authors with United States citizenship without a Goodreads identifier
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q5.   ?item wdt:P27 wd:Q30.   ?item wdt:P106 wd:Q36180.   MINUS { ?item wdt:P2963 ?plholder1 } . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: All events that occured on 2001/09/11
column2: PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel WHERE {   ?item  p:P585/ps:P585 "2001-09-11T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime. ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Works by women that were born between 1800 and 1900, are in the WomenWriters database and are translated
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> SELECT ?translator ?translatorLabel ?work ?workLabel ?author ?authorLabel WHERE {     ?work wdt:P655 ?translator;           wdt:P50 ?author.     ?author wdt:P2533 ?wid;             wdt:P21 wd:Q6581072;             wdt:P569 ?birth .     FILTER (?birth > "1800-01-01"^^xsd:dateTime)     FILTER (?birth < "1900-01-01"^^xsd:dateTime)     ?work rdfs:label ?workLabel . FILTER (LANG(?workLabel) = "en") .     ?translator rdfs:label ?translatorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?translatorLabel) = "en") .     ?author rdfs:label ?authorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?authorLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Timeline of albums by Manu Chao and Mano Negra
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?album ?performerLabel ?albumLabel ?publication_date WHERE {   VALUES ?performer {       wd:Q936474       wd:Q207898     }    ?album wdt:P175 ?performer ;       wdt:P577 ?publication_date . ?album rdfs:label ?albumLabel . FILTER (LANG(?albumLabel) = "en") . ?performer rdfs:label ?performerLabel . FILTER (LANG(?performerLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Most popular tonality
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?tonalityLabel (COUNT(?tonalityLabel) AS ?count) WHERE {   ?work wdt:P826 ?tonality. ?tonality rdfs:label ?tonalityLabel . FILTER (LANG(?tonalityLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?tonalityLabel ORDER BY DESC(?count)

column1: Music composers by birth place
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?_coordinates ?_image WHERE {   ?item wdt:P106 wd:Q36834;         wdt:P18 ?_image;         wdt:P19/wdt:P625 ?_coordinates. ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Composers and their most-used tonality
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?composerLabel ?tonalityLabel ?count WHERE {   {     SELECT ?composer (MAX(?count) AS ?count_)     WHERE     {       {         SELECT ?composer ?tonality (COUNT(?composition) AS ?count)         WHERE         {           ?composition wdt:P86 ?composer;                        wdt:P826 ?tonality.         }         GROUP BY ?composer ?tonality         HAVING(?count > 1)       }     }     GROUP BY ?composer   }   {     SELECT ?composer ?tonality (COUNT(?composition) AS ?count)     WHERE     {       ?composition wdt:P86 ?composer;                    wdt:P826 ?tonality.     }     GROUP BY ?composer ?tonality     HAVING(?count > 1)   } ?composer rdfs:label ?composerLabel . FILTER (LANG(?composerLabel) = "en") . ?tonality rdfs:label ?tonalityLabel . FILTER (LANG(?tonalityLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?count)

column1: Songs with longest melody
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?song ?songLabel ?code WHERE {   ?song wdt:P1236 ?code. ?song rdfs:label ?songLabel . FILTER (LANG(?songLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC(?code) LIMIT 10

column1: How many musicians dies at certain age
column2: PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>     SELECT (COUNT (DISTINCT ?a) AS ?count) WHERE {         ?a wdt:P31 wd:Q5 .         ?a wdt:P106/wdt:P279 wd:Q639669 .         ?a p:P569/psv:P569 ?birth_date_node .         ?a p:P570/psv:P570 ?death_date_node .         ?birth_date_node wikibase:timeValue ?birth_date .         ?death_date_node wikibase:timeValue ?death_date .                       }

column1: Musicians born in Rotterdam (the Netherlands)
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?itemDescription WHERE {     ?item wdt:P106/wdt:P279* wd:Q639669 .     ?item wdt:P19/wdt:P131* wd:Q34370 . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Paintings depicting woodwind instruments
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?object ?objectLabel ?image WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q3305213 .   ?item wdt:P180 ?object .   ?object wdt:P279+ wd:Q181247 .   ?item wdt:P18 ?image . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . ?object rdfs:label ?objectLabel . FILTER (LANG(?objectLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Paintings depicting musical instruments with some connection to Hamburg
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?image WHERE {      ?object wdt:P279+ wd:Q34379 .   ?item wdt:P180 ?object .   ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q3305213 .   ?item wdt:P18 ?image .   ?item ?prop ?hhlink .   ?hhlink ?prop2 wd:Q1055 . }

column1: Public sculptures in Paris
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item  ?Titre ?createur ?date ?image ?coord WHERE {    ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q860861.    ?item wdt:P136 wd:Q557141 .    {?item wdt:P131 wd:Q90.}    UNION    {?item wdt:P131 ?arr.    ?arr wdt:P131 wd:Q90. }    ?item rdfs:label ?Titre . FILTER (lang(?Titre) = "fr").    OPTIONAL {?item wdt:P170 ?Qcreateur.    ?Qcreateur rdfs:label ?createur . FILTER (lang(?createur) = "fr") .}    OPTIONAL {?item wdt:P571 ?date.}    OPTIONAL {?item wdt:P18  ?image.}    OPTIONAL {?item wdt:P625 ?coord.} }

column1: Locations of Pablo Picasso works
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?label ?coord ?subj WHERE {    ?subj wdt:P170 wd:Q5593 .   OPTIONAL {?subj wdt:P276 ?loc .     ?loc wdt:P625 ?coord } .    ?subj rdfs:label ?label . FILTER (lang(?label) = "en") }

column1: Eiffel Tower in art
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?instanceLabel ?creatorLabel ?date ?image WHERE {   ?item wdt:P180 wd:Q243 .   ?item wdt:P31 ?instance .   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P170 ?creator . ?creator rdfs:label ?creatorLabel . FILTER (LANG(?creatorLabel) = "en") . }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P571 ?date }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P18 ?image } ?instance rdfs:label ?instanceLabel . FILTER (LANG(?instanceLabel) = "en") . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?itemLabel

column1: Paintings by Gustav Klimt
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT ?item ?pic WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q3305213 .   ?item wdt:P170 wd:Q34661 .   ?item wdt:P18 ?pic . }

column1: Map of all the paintings for which we know a location with the count per location
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?locationLabel ?coord (COUNT(?painting) AS ?count) WHERE {     ?painting wdt:P31 wd:Q3305213 .     ?painting wdt:P276 ?location .    ?location wdt:P625 ?coord. ?location rdfs:label ?locationLabel . FILTER (LANG(?locationLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?locationLabel ?coord

column1: Versions of The Scream
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?item ?itemL ?date ?typeL ?collectionL ?img ?materialL WHERE {   ?item wdt:P179 wd:Q471379 .   ?item wdt:P18 ?img .   ?item wdt:P571 ?date .   ?item wdt:P31 ?instance .   ?item rdfs:label ?itemL . FILTER (lang(?itemL) = "en").   ?instance rdfs:label ?typeL . FILTER (lang(?typeL) = "en").   OPTIONAL {     ?item wdt:P195 ?collection .     ?collection rdfs:label ?collectionL . FILTER (lang(?collectionL) = "en").   }   OPTIONAL {     ?item wdt:P186 ?material .     ?material rdfs:label ?materialL . FILTER (lang(?materialL) = "en").   } } ORDER BY ?date ?item ?itemL

column1: Depicted objects in art work
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?depicts (SAMPLE(?dL) AS ?depictsLabel) (COUNT(DISTINCT ?item) AS ?count) WHERE {    ?item wdt:P180 ?depicts .    OPTIONAL { ?depicts rdfs:label ?dL . FILTER (lang(?dL) = "en")  } } GROUP BY ?depicts ORDER BY DESC(?count) ?depictsLabel

column1: Monuments historiques in Loire-Atlantique
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?communeLabel (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?merimee_; SEPARATOR = ", ") AS ?merimee) ?coords ?image WHERE {   {     SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?merimee_ WHERE {       ?item wdt:P1435/wdt:P279* wd:Q916475 .       ?item p:P1435 ?heritage_statement .              ?item wdt:P380 ?merimee_ .     }     ORDER BY ?merimee_   }   ?item wdt:P131/wdt:P131* wd:Q3068 .   ?item wdt:P131 ?commune .   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P625 ?coords . }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P18 ?image . } ?commune rdfs:label ?communeLabel . FILTER (LANG(?communeLabel) = "en") . ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel ?communeLabel ?coords ?image ORDER BY ?communeLabel ?itemLabel

column1: Sculptures by Max Bill
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?countryLabel ?placeLabel ?date ?coords ?image WHERE {   ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q860861 .   ?item wdt:P170 wd:Q123454 .   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P17 ?country . ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel . FILTER (LANG(?countryLabel) = "en") . }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P131 ?place . ?place rdfs:label ?placeLabel . FILTER (LANG(?itemLabel) = "en") . } ORDER BY ?itemLabel ?placeLabel

column1: Authority control properties usage for paintings

FILTER (LANG(?propertyLabel) = "en") .   ?property schema:description ?propertyDescription . FILTER (LANG(?propertyDescription) = "en") . } GROUP BY ?propertyLabel ?propertyDescription ORDER BY DESC (?count) LIMIT 100

FILTER (LANG(?propertyLabel) = "en") .   ?property schema:description ?propertyDescription . FILTER (LANG(?propertyDescription) = "en") . } ORDER BY DESC (?count) LIMIT 100

FILTER (LANG(?paintingLabel) = "en") . }

column1: Public art in Paris
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT   ?item   (SAMPLE (?titleL) AS ?title)   (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?creatorL ; SEPARATOR = ", ") AS ?creator)   (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?genreL ; SEPARATOR = ", ") AS ?genre)   (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?placeL ; SEPARATOR = ", ") AS ?place)   (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?arrL ; SEPARATOR = ", ") AS ?arrondissement)   (SAMPLE (?img) AS ?image)   (SAMPLE (?coord) AS ?coordinates) WHERE {     {       SELECT DISTINCT ?item WHERE { {         ?item wdt:P136 wd:Q557141 ;               wdt:P131 wd:Q90       } UNION {         ?item wdt:P136 wd:Q557141 ;               wdt:P131/wdt:P131* wd:Q90       } }     }     OPTIONAL { ?item rdfs:label ?titleL . FILTER (lang(?titleL) = "fr") }     OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P170 ?plholder1 .                ?plholder1 rdfs:label ?creatorL.                FILTER (lang(?creatorL) = "fr") }     OPTIONAL {       {         ?item wdt:P136 ?g .        } UNION {         ?item wdt:P31 ?g .       }       ?g rdfs:label ?genreL . FILTER (lang(?genreL) = "fr") .     }     OPTIONAL {       ?item wdt:P276 ?plholder2 .       ?plholder2 rdfs:label ?placeL.       FILTER (lang(?placeL) = "fr") .     }     OPTIONAL {       ?item wdt:P131 ?plholder3 .       ?plholder3 wdt:P131 wd:Q90 ; rdfs:label ?arrL .       FILTER (lang(?arrL) = "fr").            }     OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P18 ?img }     OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P625 ?coord } } GROUP BY ?item

column1: Get the CIViC citation corpus
column2: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pr: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/reference/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> SELECT DISTINCT ?pmid ?citation ?citationLabel WHERE {    VALUES ?predictor {p:P3354 p:P3355 p:P3356 p:P3357 p:P3358 p:P3359 }     ?item p:P3329 ?civicId  ;           ?predictor ?predictor_value .     ?civicId ps:P3329 ?id .     ?predictor_value prov:wasDerivedFrom ?reference .     ?reference pr:P248 ?citation .     ?citation wdt:P698 ?pmid . ?citation rdfs:label ?citationLabel . FILTER (LANG(?citationLabel) = "en") . }

column1: English common names and information for animals given their scientific names
column2: PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/> PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?scientific_name ?common_name ?length ?life_expectency ?height ?wing_span ?mass WHERE {   ?item wdt:P225 ?scientific_name;     wdt:P1843 ?common_name.   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P2043 ?length. }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P2250 ?life_expectency. }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P2048 ?height. }   OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:P2050 ?wing_span. }   OPTIONAL {     ?item p:P2067 ?mass_statement_node.     ?mass_statement_node pq:P642 wd:Q78101716;       ps:P2067 ?mass.   }   FILTER(LANG(?common_name) = "en")   FILTER regex(?scientific_name, "mustela erminea|aquila adalberti|vespula germanica|accipiter nisus|buteo buteo", "i") }
